                  </persName> was indicted<rs id="t18530704-781-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18530704-781-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18530704-781-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp> for a like offence.</rs>
